      "value": "<p>Your eye magnifies distant targets as well as a scope. You can adjust your sight in that eye as a single action to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.BlAOM2X92SI6HMtJ]{Seek} a specific creature with a +2 circumstance bonus to your Perception check, or Seek to search a 10-foot square up to 100 feet away for any undetected or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.iU0fEDdBp3rXpTMC]{Hidden} creatures or objects. You don't take penalties for an object or creature being too far away unless you are more than 2 miles away.</p>"
